data.description: Beautiful Newer home within walking distance to some of the county's TOP SCHOOLS! , Floor plan features 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, 2 car garage, IMPACT WINDOWS and SLIDERS, tile throughout, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, gorgeous kitchen cabinets, vaulted ceilings in the main living area, lanai off the great room, split bedrooms, floritam sod with automated sprinkler system, plenty of room for a pool and play area for the kids or pets. Close proximity to Sunsplash Family Waterpark, great dining and shopping. Easy drive to some of the state's most beautiful beaches as well as Downtown Cape Coral and Ft. Myers. Call to schedule a private showing today.
